name: Pisah
description: Sometimes the greatest act of love is to walk away , so that the other person can find their true self and direction again. Learning to walk away is hard but staying to suffer is harder. It may not be a matter of life or death, but staying stuck will certainly starve your soul and injure your heart. Don't waste your energy trying to force something that isn't mean to be. let them find them and let you find you!
